\u064b\\u060c \\u0641\\u0625\\u0646\\u0647 \\u064a\\u0643\\u0648\\u0646 \\u0645\\u062c\\u0647\\u0632\\u0627\\u064b \\u0628\\u0634\\u0643\\u0644 \\u0623\\u0641\\u0636\\u0644 \\u0644\\u0644\\u0647\\u0631\\u0648\\u0628 \\u0645\\u0646 \\u062d\\u0644\\u0642\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0641\\u0642\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0641\\u0631\\u063a\\u0629\\u060c \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u0627\\u0647\\u0645\\u0629 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0645\\u062c\\u062a\\u0645\\u0639\\u0627\\u062a\\u0647\\u060c \\u0648\\u0641\\u064a \\u0646\\u0647\\u0627\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0637\\u0627\\u0641 \\u0631\\u0641\\u0639 \\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u0648\\u064a\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0639\\u064a\\u0634\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0623\\u0645\\u062a\\u0647 \\u0628\\u0623\\u0643\\u0645\\u0644\\u0647\\u0627.<\\/p>"}}}','image' => 'b23a826c-3756-4d88-bbc1-59af57192bcf.webp','status' => '1','created_at' => '2023-11-04 16:57:33','updated_at' => '2023-11-04 16:57:33'),
            array('id' => '3','admin_id' => '1','title' => '{"language":{"en":{"title":"Collect Donation For Sudan\'s School & Hospital"},"es":{"title":"Recaudar donaci\\u00f3n para la escuela y el hospital de Sud\\u00e1n"},"ar":{"title":"\\u062c\\u0645\\u0639 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0628\\u0631\\u0639\\u0627\\u062a \\u0644\\u0645\\u062f\\u0631\\u0633\\u0629 \\u0648\\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u0634\\u0641\\u0649 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0633\\u0648\\u062f\\u0627\\u0646"}}}','slug' => 'collect-donation-for-sudans-school-hospital','our_goal' => '28000.00','raised' => '0.00','to_go' => '28000.00','desc' => '{"language":{"en":{"desc":"<p>In the heart of Africa, the nation of Sudan is facing critical challenges, with a pressing need for assistance in two fundamental sectors: education and healthcare. The people of Sudan are resilient and hopeful, but they lack access to quality education and healthcare facilities that many of us often take for granted. Today, we are reaching out to you to support a crucial initiative that aims to improve the lives of countless Sudanese citizens. Your generous donations will contribute to the construction and improvement of schools and hospitals in Sudan, providing a brighter future for those in need.<\\/p><p>**Education for a Brighter Tomorrow**<\\/p><p>Sudan\'s education system has been grappling with underfunding, inadequate infrastructure, and a shortage of qualified teachers for years. This situation has left countless children without access to quality education, depriving them of opportunities to escape the cycle of poverty and build a better future for themselves and their communities.<\\/p><p>With your support, we aim to build and renovate schools, ensuring they are equipped with modern facilities, including classrooms, libraries, and computer labs. These facilities will not only provide a safe and conducive learning environment but also help bridge the educational gap that has plagued Sudan for generations. Furthermore, we will train and recruit qualified teachers to ensure that every child receives a quality education.<\\/p><p>**Improving Healthcare Access**<\\/p><p>Access to healthcare is a basic human right, but in Sudan, millions of people lack the necessary medical care. Hospitals and clinics are often overcrowded, ill-equipped, and understaffed, making it challenging for individuals to receive the care they need. Your donations will help transform the healthcare landscape in Sudan.<\\/p><p>We are committed to building new hospitals and upgrading existing facilities, stocking them with modern medical equipment and ensuring they are staffed with well-trained healthcare professionals. These improvements will save lives, reduce suffering, and bring hope to those who have long been neglected by the healthcare system.<\\/p>"},"es":{"desc":"<p>En el coraz\\u00f3n de \\u00c1frica, la naci\\u00f3n de Sud\\u00e1n enfrenta desaf\\u00edos cr\\u00edticos, con una necesidad apremiante de asistencia en dos sectores fundamentales: educaci\\u00f3n y atenci\\u00f3n m\\u00e9dica. El pueblo de Sud\\u00e1n es resiliente y esperanzado, pero carece de acceso a una educaci\\u00f3n de calidad y a instalaciones sanitarias que muchos de nosotros a menudo damos por sentado. Hoy nos acercamos a usted para apoyar una iniciativa crucial que tiene como objetivo mejorar las vidas de innumerables ciudadanos sudaneses. Sus generosas donaciones contribuir\\u00e1n a la construcci\\u00f3n y mejora de escuelas y hospitales en Sud\\u00e1n, brindando un futuro mejor a quienes lo necesitan.<\\/p><p>**Educaci\\u00f3n para un ma\\u00f1ana mejor**<\\/p><p>El sistema educativo de Sud\\u00e1n ha estado lidiando con falta de financiaci\\u00f3n, infraestructura inadecuada y escasez de docentes calificados durante a\\u00f1os. Esta situaci\\u00f3n ha dejado a innumerables ni\\u00f1os sin acceso a una educaci\\u00f3n de calidad, priv\\u00e1ndolos de oportunidades para escapar del ciclo de la pobreza y construir un futuro mejor para ellos y sus comunidades.<\\/p><p>Con su apoyo, nuestro objetivo es construir y renovar escuelas, asegur\\u00e1ndonos de que est\\u00e9n equipadas con instalaciones modernas, incluidas aulas, bibliotecas y laboratorios de computaci\\u00f3n. Estas instalaciones no s\\u00f3lo proporcionar\\u00e1n un entorno de aprendizaje seguro y propicio, sino que tambi\\u00e9n ayudar\\u00e1n a cerrar la brecha educativa que ha afectado a Sud\\u00e1n durante generaciones. Adem\\u00e1s, capacitaremos y contrataremos maestros calificados para garantizar que todos los ni\\u00f1os reciban una educaci\\u00f3n de calidad.<\\/p><p>**Mejorando el acceso a la atenci\\u00f3n m\\u00e9dica**<\\/p><p>El acceso a la atenci\\u00f3n sanitaria es un derecho humano b\\u00e1sico, pero en Sud\\u00e1n millones de personas carecen de la atenci\\u00f3n m\\u00e9dica necesaria. Los hospitales y cl\\u00ednicas suelen estar superpoblados, mal equipados y con poco personal, lo que dificulta que las personas reciban la atenci\\u00f3n que necesitan. Sus donaciones ayudar\\u00e1n a transformar el panorama sanitario en Sud\\u00e1n.<\\/p><p>Estamos comprometidos a construir nuevos hospitales y mejorar las instalaciones existentes, dot\\u00e1ndolas de equipos m\\u00e9dicos modernos y garantizando que cuenten con profesionales de la salud bien capacitados. Estas mejoras salvar\\u00e1n vidas, reducir\\u00e1n el sufrimiento y traer\\u00e1n esperanza a quienes durante mucho tiempo han sido desatendidos por el sistema de salud.<\\/p>"},"ar":{"desc":"<p>\\u0641\\u064a \\u0642\\u0644\\u0628 \\u0623\\u0641\\u0631\\u064a\\u0642\\u064a\\u0627\\u060c \\u062a\\u0648\\u0627\\u062c\\u0647 \\u062f\\u0648\\u0644\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0633\\u0648\\u062f\\u0627\\u0646 \\u062a\\u062d\\u062f\\u064a\\u0627\\u062a \\u062d\\u0631\\u062c\\u0629\\u060c \\u0645\\u0639 \\u062d\\u0627\\u062c\\u0629 \\u0645\\u0644\\u062d\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u0627\\u0639\\u062f\\u0629 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0642\\u0637\\u0627\\u0639\\u064a\\u0646 \\u0623\\u0633\\u