            array('id' => '4','admin_id' => '1','title' => '{"language":{"en":{"title":"Gift An Education... Make a Life Better!"},"es":{"title":"Regala una educaci\\u00f3n... \\u00a1Haz una vida mejor!"},"ar":{"title":"\\u0647\\u062f\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0639\\u0644\\u064a\\u0645... \\u0627\\u062c\\u0639\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062d\\u064a\\u0627\\u0629 \\u0623\\u0641\\u0636\\u0644!"}}}','slug' => 'gift-an-education-make-a-life-better','our_goal' => '28000.00','raised' => '0.00','to_go' => '28000.00','desc' => '{"language":{"en":{"desc":"<p>In a world where the value of education is immeasurable, the adage \\"knowledge is power\\" holds truer than ever before. Education is not merely the gateway to a brighter future; it is the key to unlocking a world of opportunities, personal growth, and positive change. By gifting someone the opportunity to learn, you have the power to make a significant and lasting impact on their life.<\\/p><p>Imagine a world where every child, regardless of their background, has access to quality education. This vision is more attainable than we might think, and it starts with the simple act of gifting education. Whether you\'re considering investing in a child\'s academic journey, supporting an adult\'s quest for new skills, or contributing to a community\'s educational infrastructure, the ripple effects of your gift can be profound.<\\/p><p>Education equips individuals with the tools they need to build better lives for themselves and their communities. It instills the power of critical thinking, problem-solving, and creativity. A well-rounded education opens doors to a wide range of career opportunities, improving one\'s employability and earning potential. But education is about more than just finding a job; it fosters personal development, self-confidence, and a sense of purpose. It empowers individuals to make informed choices and advocate for their rights, ultimately strengthening their voices in society.<\\/p><p>For a child in a disadvantaged community, the gift of education is a lifeline. It provides hope and a path out of poverty. With access to quality schooling, children can break free from the cycle of limited opportunities and build brighter futures for themselves and their families. By gifting education, you provide them with the chance to dream, to aim high, and to believe in their own potential.<\\/p><p>Adult learners also benefit immensely from educational opportunities. Many individuals yearn to improve their skills, change careers, or pursue their passions, but are held back by financial constraints. Your gift of education can remove these barriers, enabling adults to follow their dreams and better their lives.<\\/p><p>In addition to personal transformation, education has the power to uplift entire communities. By investing in schools, scholarships, and educational resources, you help build a more knowledgeable and capable workforce. This, in turn, stimulates economic growth, reduces crime rates, and creates a healthier and more vibrant society..<\\/p>"},"es":{"desc":"<p>En un mundo donde el valor de la educaci\\u00f3n es inmensurable, el dicho \\"el conocimiento es poder\\" es m\\u00e1s cierto que nunca. La educaci\\u00f3n no es simplemente la puerta de entrada a un futuro mejor; es la clave para desbloquear un mundo de oportunidades, crecimiento personal y cambios positivos. Al brindarle a alguien la oportunidad de aprender, usted tiene el poder de generar un impacto significativo y duradero en su vida.<\\/p><p>Imaginemos un mundo en el que todos los ni\\u00f1os, independientemente de su origen, tengan acceso a una educaci\\u00f3n de calidad. Esta visi\\u00f3n es m\\u00e1s alcanzable de lo que podr\\u00edamos pensar y comienza con el simple acto de regalar educaci\\u00f3n. Ya sea que est\\u00e9 considerando invertir en el recorrido acad\\u00e9mico de un ni\\u00f1o, apoyar la b\\u00fasqueda de nuevas habilidades de un adulto o contribuir a la infraestructura educativa de una comunidad, el efecto domin\\u00f3 de su donaci\\u00f3n puede ser profundo.<\\/p><p>La educaci\\u00f3n proporciona a las personas las herramientas que necesitan para construir una vida mejor para ellos y sus comunidades. Inculca el poder del pensamiento cr\\u00edtico, la resoluci\\u00f3n de problemas y la creatividad. Una educaci\\u00f3n integral abre las puertas a una amplia gama de oportunidades profesionales, mejorando la empleabilidad y el potencial de ingresos. Pero la educaci\\u00f3n es algo m\\u00e1s que simplemente encontrar un trabajo; Fomenta el desarrollo personal, la confianza en uno mismo y un sentido de prop\\u00f3sito. Empodera a las personas para tomar decisiones informadas y defender sus derechos, fortaleciendo en \\u00faltima instancia sus voces en la sociedad.<\\/p><p>Para un ni\\u00f1o de una comunidad desfavorecida, el don de la educaci\\u00f3n es un salvavidas. Proporciona esperanza y un camino para salir de la pobreza. Con acceso a una educaci\\u00f3n de calidad, los ni\\u00f1os pueden liberarse del ciclo de oportunidades limitadas y construir futuros m\\u00e1s brillantes para ellos y sus familias. Al regalar educaci\\u00f3n, les brindas la oportunidad de so\\u00f1ar, apuntar alto y creer en su propio potencial.<\\/p><p>Los estudiantes adultos tambi\\u00e9n se benefician enormemente de las oportunidades educativas. Muchas personas anhelan mejorar sus habilidades, cambiar de carrera o perseguir sus pasiones, pero se ven frenadas por limitaciones financieras. Su don de educaci\\u00f3n puede eliminar estas barreras, permitiendo a los adultos seguir sus sue\\u00f1os y mejorar sus vidas.<\\/p><p>Adem\\u00e1s de la transformaci\\u00f3n personal, la educaci\\u00f3n tiene el poder de elevar a comunidades enteras. Al invertir en escuelas, becas y recursos educativos, ayuda a crear una fuerza laboral con m\\u00e1s conocimientos y capacidad. Esto, a su vez, estimula el crecimiento econ\\u00f3mico, reduce las tasas de criminalidad y crea una sociedad m\\u00e1s sana y vibrante.<\\/p>"},"ar":{"desc":"<p>\\u0641\\u064a \\u0639\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645 \\u062d\\u064a\\u062b \\u0642\\u064a\\u0645\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0639\\u0644\\u064a\\u0645 \\u0644\\u0627 \\u062a\\u0642\\u062f\\u0631 \\u0628\\u062b\\u0645\\u0646\\u060c \\u0641\\u0625\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0642\\u0648\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0623\\u062b\\u0648\\u0631 \\"\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0639\\u0631\\u0641\\u0629 \\u0642\\u0648\\u0629\\" \\u0623\\u0635\\u0628\\u062d \\u0623\\u0643\\u062b\\u0631 \\u0635\\u062f\\u0642\\u0627 \\u0645\\u0646 \\u0623\\u064a \\u0648\\u0642\\u062a \\u0645\\u0636\\u0649. \\u0625\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0639\\u0644\\u064a\\u0645 \\u0644\\u064a\\u0633 \\u0645\\u062c\\u0631\\u062f \\u0628\\u0648\\u0627\\u0628\\u0629 \\u0625\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u0642\\u0628\\u0644 \\u0623\\u0643\\u062b\\u0631 \\u0625\\u0634\\u0631\\u0627\\u0642\\u0627\\u061b \\u0625\\u0646\\u0647 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0641\\u062a\\u0627\\u062d \\u0644\\u0641\\u062a\\u062d \\u0639\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645 \\u0645\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0641\\u0631\\u0635 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0646\\u0645\\u0648 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0634\\u062e\\u0635\\u064a \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u063a\\u064a\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0625\\u064a\\u062c\\u0627\\u0628\\u064a. \\u0645\\u0646 \\u062e\\u0644\\u0627\\u0644 \\u0645\\u0646\\u062d \\u0634\\u062e\\u0635 \\u0645\\u0627 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0641\\u0631\\u0635\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0644\\u062a\\u0639\\u0644\\u0645\\u060c \\u0644\\u062f\\u064a\\u0643 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0642\\u062f\\u0631\\u0629 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0625\\u062d\\u062f\\u0627\\u062b \\u062a\\u0623\\u062b\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0643\\u0628\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0648\\u062f\\u0627\\u0626\\u0645 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u062d\\u064a\\u0627\\u062a\\u0647.<\\/p><p>\\u062a\\u062e\\u064a\\u0644 \\u0639\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0627 \\u064a\\u0633\\u062a\\u0637\\u064a\\u0639 \\u0641\\u064a\\u0647 \\u0643\\u0644 \\u0637\\u0641\\u0644\\u060c \\u0628\\u063a\\u0636 \\u