5\\u0646\\u0647\\u062c\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0647\\u0648\\u0627\\u064a\\u0627\\u062a \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0646\\u0627\\u0641\\u0630 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0625\\u0628\\u062f\\u0627\\u0639\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0628\\u0646\\u0641\\u0633 \\u0623\\u0647\\u0645\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0639\\u0644\\u064a\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0631\\u0633\\u0645\\u064a. \\u062a\\u0633\\u0627\\u0639\\u062f \\u0647\\u0630\\u0647 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u062c\\u0627\\u0631\\u0628 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0637\\u0641\\u0627\\u0644 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0627\\u0643\\u062a\\u0634\\u0627\\u0641 \\u0634\\u063a\\u0641\\u0647\\u0645 \\u0648\\u062a\\u0637\\u0648\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0645\\u0647\\u0627\\u0631\\u0627\\u062a\\u0647\\u0645 \\u0648\\u0628\\u0646\\u0627\\u0621 \\u0634\\u0639\\u0648\\u0631 \\u0628\\u0627\\u0644\\u0647\\u0648\\u064a\\u0629.<\\/p>"}}}','image' => '1f927086-8f4f-4116-bfe2-bf661436f3e4.webp','status' => '1','created_at' => '2023-11-04 16:54:05','updated_at' => '2023-11-04 16:54:05'),
            array('id' => '6','admin_id' => '1','title' => '{"language":{"en":{"title":"Help These Children Find Their Smiles"},"es":{"title":"Ayuda a estas ni\\u00f1as a encontrar sus sonrisas"},"ar":{"title":"\\u0633\\u0627\\u0639\\u062f \\u0647\\u0624\\u0644\\u0627\\u0621 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0637\\u0641\\u0627\\u0644 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0639\\u062b\\u0648\\u0631 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0627\\u0628\\u062a\\u0633\\u0627\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a\\u0647\\u0645"}}}','slug' => 'help-these-children-find-their-smiles','our_goal' => '28000.00','raised' => '0.00','to_go' => '28000.00','desc' => '{"language":{"en":{"desc":"<p>In a world often marked by adversity and challenges, there are countless children who bear the weight of their circumstances, their smiles hidden beneath layers of hardship, sorrow, and despair. These children, vulnerable and often forgotten, need our support, love, and compassion to help them rediscover their joy and find their smiles once again.<\\/p><p>Childhood should be a time of innocence, wonder, and unfettered happiness. Yet, for many, it is marred by circumstances beyond their control. Poverty, conflict, illness, and neglect shroud their lives, leaving them in a state of perpetual darkness. It is our collective responsibility to extend a helping hand and illuminate their path towards a brighter future.<\\/p><p>The journey to help these children find their smiles begins with the recognition of their inherent resilience and potential. Despite their circumstances, they possess an incredible capacity to heal and grow. By acknowledging their strength, we empower them to take the first steps on their path to recovery.<\\/p><p>Access to education is a fundamental right that can pave the way for these children to find their smiles. Education not only equips them with knowledge and skills but also instills hope and ambition. By supporting educational initiatives, we provide them with the tools to break free from the cycle of poverty and adversity, helping them to envision a brighter future.<\\/p><p>Healthcare is another critical aspect of their journey. Many children suffer from illness and malnutrition, depriving them of the chance to live a healthy and fulfilling life. Through medical care and nutrition programs, we can address their immediate needs, enabling them to grow and thrive. As their physical health improves, so does their emotional well-being, allowing their smiles to shine through.<\\/p><p>Emotional support is essential in the quest to help these children find their smiles. Many have endured trauma and loss that leaves lasting scars. By providing them with a safe and nurturing environment, offering counseling and psychological support, and fostering a sense of belonging, we can help them heal and build resilience.<\\/p><p>The power of play and creativity should not be underestimated. Play is a universal language of childhood, allowing children to express themselves, explore their world, and process their emotions. By providing safe spaces for play and creative expression, we give these children the opportunity to let their smiles emerge, one joyful moment at a time.<\\/p>"},"es":{"desc":"<p>En un mundo a menudo marcado por la adversidad y los desaf\\u00edos, hay innumerables ni\\u00f1os que soportan el peso de sus circunstancias, con sus sonrisas escondidas bajo capas de dificultades, tristeza y desesperaci\\u00f3n. Estos ni\\u00f1os, vulnerables y a menudo olvidados, necesitan nuestro apoyo, amor y compasi\\u00f3n para ayudarlos a redescubrir su alegr\\u00eda y encontrar sus sonrisas una vez m\\u00e1s.<\\/p><p>La infancia deber\\u00eda ser una \\u00e9poca de inocencia, asombro y felicidad ilimitada. Sin embargo, para muchos, esto se ve empa\\u00f1ado por circunstancias que escapan a su control. La pobreza, los conflictos, las enfermedades y el abandono envuelven sus vidas, dej\\u00e1ndolos en un estado de oscuridad perpetua. Es nuestra responsabilidad colectiva extender una mano amiga e iluminar su camino hacia un futuro mejor.<\\/p><p>El camino para ayudar a estos ni\\u00f1os a encontrar su sonrisa comienza con el reconocimiento de su resiliencia y potencial inherentes. A pesar de sus circunstancias, poseen una incre\\u00edble capacidad para sanar y crecer. Al reconocer su fortaleza, les damos el poder para dar los primeros pasos en su camino hacia la recuperaci\\u00f3n.<\\/p><p>El acceso a la educaci\\u00f3n es un derecho fundamental que puede allanar el camino para que estos ni\\u00f1os encuentren su sonrisa. La educaci\\u00f3n no s\\u00f3lo les proporciona conocimientos y habilidades, sino que tambi\\u00e9n les infunde esperanza y ambici\\u00f3n. Al apoyar iniciativas educativas, les brindamos las herramientas para liberarse del ciclo de pobreza y adversidad, ayud\\u00e1ndolos a imaginar un futuro mejor.<\\/p><p>La atenci\\u00f3n m\\u00e9dica es otro aspecto cr\\u00edtico de su viaje. Muchos ni\\u00f1os sufren enfermedades y desnutrici\\u00f3n, lo que les priva de la oportunidad de vivir una vida sana y plena. A trav\\u00e9s de programas de atenci\\u00f3n m\\u00e9dica y nutrici\\u00f3n, podemos abordar sus necesidades inmediatas, permiti\\u00e9ndoles crecer y prosperar. A medida que mejora su salud f\\u00edsica, tambi\\u00e9n mejora su bienestar emocional, lo que permite que sus sonrisas brillen.<\\/p><p>El apoyo emocional es esencial en la b\\u00fasqueda de ayudar a estos ni\\u00f1os a encontrar su sonrisa. Muchos han sufrido traumas y p\\u00e9rdidas que dejan cicatrices duraderas. Al brindarles un entorno seguro y enriquecedor, ofrecerles asesoramiento y apoyo psicol\\u00f3gico y fomentar un sentido de pertenencia, podemos ayudarlos a sanar y desarrollar resiliencia.<\\/p><p>No se debe subestimar el poder del juego y la creatividad. El juego es un lenguaje universal de la infancia que permite a los ni\\u00f1os expresarse, explorar su mundo y procesar sus emociones. Al brindarles espacios seguros para el juego y la expresi\\u00f3n creativa, les brindamos a estos ni\\u00f1os la oportunidad de dejar que sus sonrisas emerjan, un momento de alegr\\u00eda a la vez.<\\/p>"},"ar":{"desc":"<p>\\u0641\\u064a \\u0639\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645 \\u064a\\u062a\\u0633\\u0645 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0643\\u062b\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0645\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u062d\\u064a\\u0627\\u0646 \\u0628\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u062d\\u0646 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u062d\\u062f\\u064a\\u0627\\u062a\\u060c \\u0647\\u0646\\u0627\\u0643 \\u0639\\u062f\\u062f \\u0644\\u0627 \\u064a\\u062d\\u0635\\u0649 \\u0645\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0637\\u0641\\u0627\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0630\\u064a\\u0646 \\u064a\\u062a\\u062d\\u0645\\u0644\\u0648\\u0646 \\u062b\\u0642\\u0644 \\u0638\\u0631\\u0648\\u0641\\u0647\\u0645\\u060c \\u0648\\u062a\\u062e\\u062a\\u0628\\u0626 \\u0627\\u0628\\u062a\\u0633\\u0627\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a\\u0647\\u0645 \\u062a\\u062d\\u062a \\u0637\\u0628\\u0642\\u0627\\u062a \\u0645\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0634\\u0642\\u0629 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u062d\\u0632\\u0646 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u064a\\u0623\\u0633. \\u064a\\u062d\\u062a\\u0627\\u062c \\u0647\\u0624\\u0644\\u0627\\u0621 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0637\\u0641\\u0627\\u0644\\u060c \\u0627\\u0644\\u0636\\u0639\\u0641\\u0627\\u0621 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0646\\u0633\\u064a\\u0648\\u0646 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0643\\u062b\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0645\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u062d\\u064a\\u0627\\u0646\\u060c \\u0625\\u0644\\u0649 \\u062f\\u0639\\u0645\\u0646\\u0627 \\u0648\\u062d\\u0628\\u0646\\u0627 \\u0648\\u062a\\u0639\\u0627\\u0637\\u0641\\u0646\\u0627 \\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u0627\\u0639\\u062f\\u062a\\u0647\\u0645 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0625\\u0639\\u0627\\u062f\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0643\\u062a\\u0634\\u0627\\u0641 \\u0641\\u0631\\u062d\\u062a\\u0647\\u0645 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0639\\u062b\\u0648\\u0631 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0627\\u0628\\u062a\\u0633\\u0627\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a\\u0647\\u0645 \\u0645\\u0631\\u0629 \\u0623\\u062e\\u0631\\u0649.<\\/p><p>\\